    Note: HIR_IDENTIFIER (kind tag at offset 0 == 10001) it names a known
    Note: function and its identifier text lives in the HIRNode value slot
    Note: at offset 40 — this string pointer is the canonical direct-call
    Note: callee. Any other callee shape (member access, computed value, etc.)
    Note: has no static name and must be lowered as an indirect call through
    Note: the lowered callee value id.
