Note: ============================================================

@Reasoning
HIR_RANGE_EXPRESSION post: lowers a range expression (start..end
or start..=end) to a two-field range record. Allocates an inline
record holding start and end MIR values; downstream consumers
(for-each loops, slicing) read the record directly.
